{"tid":1146293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反法西斯偉大衛國戰爭勝利74周年閱兵 День Победы","createTime":"2019-05-09T07:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T09:06:28.000Z","uid":26922,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"705da9725f42a5b7c31ba3525f4a8b4009c7b721","tid":1146293,"uid":26922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:14:59.000Z","msg":"紅場閱兵<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qBYadSZOKP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqBYadSZOKP4&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=aea969f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qBYadSZOKP4</a><br />\n冬宮廣場閱兵<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PtmQri625pc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPtmQri625pc&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=2bf0ec97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PtmQri625pc</a>"},{"pid":"bf48ae46a47514b7f1bae4246624b53a1b811a3f","tid":1146293,"uid":130406,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:17:57.000Z","msg":"Heil Hitler !!<br />\nAvanti Mussolini!!"},{"pid":"b47146c24a08cab1f90279cefe8f3ebe0554d4d4","tid":1146293,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:19:39.000Z","msg":"今年好似有toyota<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a7e837cdd8c77ba3308945d86487d03c36e527","tid":1146293,"uid":26922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:22:25.000Z","msg":"維基搵到嘅有關俄羅斯(+東歐國家)歐戰勝利日<br />\nДень Победы - 勝利日，是1945年5月8日納粹德國對蘇聯正式簽訂投降書，宣佈在第二次世界大戰無條件投降（蘇聯稱為偉大的衛國戰爭）紀念日[1]。 投降書生效時歐洲中部時間為5月8日，而莫斯科時間為5月9日，因此美國及西歐國家定於每年的5月8日，俄羅斯等東歐國家定於每年的5月9日。<br />\n<br />\n每年在這天，歐洲各地，尤其是在二次大戰中勝利和曾經受納粹德國佔領和襲擊的國家，都會以不同方式紀念第二次世界大戰歐洲戰場的結束。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯由74年前第一屆羅科索夫斯基指揮嘅勝利日閱兵開始, 每年同一日都會搞勝利日閱兵, 即使蘇聯解體當年或吞併克里米亞當年, 俄羅斯窮到西咁都照搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078b754ec9cec39a0a484924b10cef050497a5c4","tid":1146293,"uid":26922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b47146c24a08cab1f90279cefe8f3ebe0554d4d4","tid":1146293,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:19:39.000Z","msg":"今年好似有toyota<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無留意"},{"pid":"23d0e8e0f3b89ae3082875121dff71c22c10e0ee","tid":1146293,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"078b754ec9cec39a0a484924b10cef050497a5c4","tid":1146293,"uid":26922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b47146c24a08cab1f90279cefe8f3ebe0554d4d4","tid":1146293,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:19:39.000Z","msg":"今年好似有toyota<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無留意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://defence-blog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Dnvb_jLv5VI-1024x646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdefence-blog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2FDnvb_jLv5VI-1024x646.jpg&h=d6188948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://defence-blog.com/army/russian-special-forces-receives-toyota-hilux-pickups.html\" da